Hakka Ampang Yong Tau Foo â€“ I tried the Yong Tau Foo along with the Wantan Pork Broth Soup, which was rich, flavorful, and fragrant. The dumplings were well-stuffed with juicy fillings, and the pork broth had a comforting depth, making it a satisfying choice. The Yong Tau Foo ingredients, including tofu, eggplant, and bitter gourd, were fresh and paired well with the soup. A great spot for authentic Hakka flavors!
